dct_title_s: Sketch showing location of properties of which search of Chain of Title desired by the Board of Commerce & Navigation, Jersey City, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Montgomery Street to 14th Street along the Hudson River in Jersey City. Map shows the grants to Nathaniel Budd and to Act of Legislature as well as pierhead and bulkhead lines.
